'''米高·羅拔·布朗'''（{{lang-en|'''Michael Robert Brown'''}}，{{bd|1977年|1月25日|catIdx=Brown, Michael}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場|中場]]，現時效力[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[韦尔港足球俱乐部|韦尔港]]。布朗攔截硬朗，在[[英超|英超]]8個球季上陣194場累計領取3面[[紅牌|紅牌]]及45面[[黃牌|黃牌]]<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.premierleague.com/page/PlayerProfile/0,,12306~8840~2009,00.html |title=Player Profile:Michael Brown |publisher=[[英超|''premierleague.com'']] |accessdate=2011-07-12 |archive-date=2010-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100728080901/http://www.premierleague.com/page/PlayerProfile/0,,12306~8840~2009,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，因而被稱為中場硬漢<ref name="wordpress2006">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://cravencottagenewsround.wordpress.com/2006/08/29/michael-brown-and-bad-tackles/ |title=Michael Brown and bad tackles « Craven Cottage Newsround |publisher=Cravencottagenewsround.wordpress.com |date=2006-08-29 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120326195634/http://cravencottagenewsround.wordpress.com/2006/08/29/michael-brown-and-bad-tackles/ |archive-date=2012-03-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.wiganlatics.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10429~8840,00.html |title=Wigan Athletic | Team | 1st Team | Michael Brown |publisher=Wiganlatics.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2011-07-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120420011009/http://www.wiganlatics.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10429~8840,00.html |archivedate=2012-04-20 }}</ref>。他曾代表[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]上陣。

==生平==
===球會===
;曼城
布朗在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[东北英格兰|東北部]][[達勒姆郡|達勒姆郡]]的[[哈特爾浦|哈特爾浦]]（Hartlepool）出生，於在學時已加入[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]青訓系統<ref>[http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/manchester_city/article5780357.ece Manchester City save best till last] {{en}}</ref>，其後與球會簽署[[職業|職業]]合約。1995年8月26日布朗首次代表一隊上陣作客對[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]，於下半場後補登場僅10多分鐘即領[[紅牌|紅牌]]遭驅逐離場<ref name="sporting-heroes1">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.sporting-heroes.net/football-heroes/displayhero_club.asp?HeroID=36497 |title=Michael Brown - Manchester City FC - Football-Heroes.net |publisher=Sporting-heroes.net |date= |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2011-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111222171657/http://sporting-heroes.net/football-heroes/displayhero_club.asp?HeroID=36497 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。當[[加利·費列哥夫|加利·費列哥夫]]（Garry Flitcroft）被賣到[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]後，布朗逐漸成為領隊[[阿倫·波爾|阿倫·波爾]]麾下一名常規正選中場球員，而他亦獲[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]徵召入伍，但曼城於球季煞科日在主場[[緬因路球場|緬因路球場]]以2-2賽和[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]後降班。曼城在新球季經歷一段動盪時期，短時間內更換5名主帥，而布朗亦失去正選席位，並被短暫分別借用到家鄉球隊[[哈特尔普尔联足球俱乐部|哈特普爾]]及[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]<ref name="wordpress2006"/><ref name="sporting-heroes1"/>。

;錫菲聯
布朗於外借[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]期間對陣[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]表現出色，獲得對手青睞而於1999年以40萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]身價正式收歸旗下，更成為領隊[[尼爾·禾諾克|尼爾·禾諾克]]（Neil Warnock）麾下一名主力球員。2002/03年球季布朗以中場球員身份在各項賽事合共轟入22球，於2003年1月17日於「[[鋼鐵之城德比|鋼鐵之城德比]]」主場對[[谢周三足球俱乐部|錫周三]]下半場離門25碼射入反超前2-1，最終3-1完場<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.sufc.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10418~18450,00.html |title=Match Report:Sheff Utd 3 - 1 Sheff Wed |publisher=[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|''sufc.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2011-07-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205012735/http://www.sufc.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10418~18450,00.html |archivedate=2012-02-05 }}</ref>；並協助球隊分別晉級[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]及[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]準決賽，而聯賽則排第3位參加升班附加賽，於準決賽對[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]兩回合各入1球累計5-3獲勝晉級決賽，他在決賽曾射失一球[[十二碼|十二碼]]，結果以0-3負於[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]而無緣升班<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.wolves.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10307~21516,00.html |title=Match Report: Sheff Utd 0 - 3 Wolverhampton |publisher=[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|''wolves.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2011-07-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110920225951/http://www.wolves.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10307~21516,00.html |archivedate=2011-09-20 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.sport.co.uk/features/Football/1589/Sportcouk_meetsEx-Wolves_goalkeeper_Matt_Murray.aspx |title=meets...Ex-Wolves goalkeeper Matt Murray |publisher=''Sport.co.uk'' |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120330080305/http://www.sport.co.uk/features/Football/1589/Sportcouk_meetsEx-Wolves_goalkeeper_Matt_Murray.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他仍獲選球會年度最佳球員<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.sufc.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10418~8840,00.html |title=Player Profiles: Michael Brown |publisher=[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|''sufc.co.uk'']] |date= |accessdate=2011-07-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100901192908/http://www.sufc.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10418~8840,00.html |archivedate=2010-09-01 }}</ref>。錫菲聯在兩項盃賽晉級途中曾分別淘汰在[[英超|英超]]開始陷於財困的[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]出局，有傳聞大舉出售球星套現減債的列斯聯有意以600萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]一同收購布朗與[[菲爾·積基爾卡|積基卡]]，但錫菲聯否認有收到列斯聯的問價<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/3153119.stm |title=Blades deny Leeds approach |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2003-08-15 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2003-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030817022300/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/3153119.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

翌季的上半季，布朗分別於對[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]及[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]的賽事領取[[紅牌|紅牌]]，而他的合約將於球季結束後屆滿，[[蘇超|蘇超]]班霸[[流浪者足球俱乐部|格拉斯哥流浪]]有意與他簽訂約前協議，於季後免費獲得布朗加盟，但錫菲聯領隊尼爾·禾諾克警告雖然球會希望布朗留隊到季尾完成合約，但如在[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]重開收到合適價錢，錫菲聯亦會將布朗出售套現<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/3307329.stm |title=Brown warning for Rangers |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2003-12-10 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2005-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051027125724/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/sheff_utd/3307329.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;熱刺
[[英超|英超]]球會[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]於2003年12月宣佈發行新股籌募1,500萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]進行收購行動，並於[[聖誕夜|聖誕前夕]]以約50萬英鎊成功羅致布朗，於2004年1月1日後進隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/t/tottenham_hotspur/3346013.stm |title=Spurs open Brown talks |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2003-12-24 |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2017-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215215807/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/t/tottenham_hotspur/3346013.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他因被罰停賽，需要等待至1月17日對[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]才首次亮相<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/t/tottenham_hotspur/3346993.stm |title=Spurs unveil Brown |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2004-01-02 |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2020-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902013502/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/t/tottenham_hotspur/3346993.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；並於2月22日主場2-2賽和[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]取得加盟後首球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3496755.stm |title=Tottenham 4-4 Leicester |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2004-02-22 |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2020-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902013153/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/3496755.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2004年至2005年英格蘭超級聯賽|翌季]]布朗在各項賽事上陣34場及射入兩球，除在聯賽作客對[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]為熱刺射入鎖定2-0勝局外<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4107393.stm |title=Norwich 0-2 Tottenham |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2004-12-26 |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2017-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215215603/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4107393.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他在較早前的[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]作客對[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]於[[加時賽|加時賽]]頂入反超前，最終以4-3將這支上屆決賽球隊淘汰出局<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/3947051.stm |title=Bolton 3-4 Tottenham (aet) |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2004-10-27 |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2020-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223174637/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/3947051.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。布朗在熱刺中場擔任的角色比在錫菲聯時稍為墮後，防守的比重越來越大，雖然其努力與忠誠獲得熱刺球迷的讚賞，但領隊[[马丁·乔尔|-{zh-hans:马丁·乔尔; zh-hk:馬田·祖爾;}-]]不斷在中場增兵，除陣中原有的[[迈克尔·卡里克|-{zh-hans:卡里克; zh-hk:卡域克;}-]]和[[杰梅恩·耶纳斯|-{zh-hans:耶纳斯; zh-hk:贊拿斯;}-]]外，再引入如[[埃德加·戴维斯|戴維斯]]、[[賀森·加利|賀森·加利]]（Hossam Ghaly）和[[丹尼·梅菲|-{zh-hans:墨菲; zh-hk:梅菲;}-]]等球員，加劇中場正選席位的競爭<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://en.eufo.de/football/squad/tottenham-hotspur/2005-06 |title=Tottenham Hotspur 2005-06 |publisher=''En.eufo.de'' |date=2005-12-31 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128135723/http://en.eufo.de/football/squad/tottenham-hotspur/2005-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2005年至2006年英格蘭超級聯賽|2005/06年球季]]上半季布朗僅獲派上陣11場，大部分以後補身份登場。

;富咸
2006年1月31日[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]關閉前布朗轉投另一支[[倫敦|倫敦]][[英超|英超]]球隊[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/f/fulham/4666572.stm |title=Fulham seal move for Spurs' Brown |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2006-01-31 |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305095050/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/f/fulham/4666572.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。布朗受傷患困擾，加入[[卡雲農舍球場|卡雲農舍球場]]初期表現並不理想，更於2006年4月1日主場1-3負於[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]的下半場雙腳飛踢[[西恩·戴维斯|桑恩·戴維斯]]而被[[球證|球證]][[基斯·科爾|科爾]]（Chris Foy）直接出示[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4842446.stm |title=Fulham 1-3 Portsmouth |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2006-04-01 |accessdate=2011-07-13 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309144410/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4842446.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。布朗於[[2006年至2007年英格蘭超級聯賽|2006/07年球季]]揭幕戰作客對[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]時<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4786577.stm |title=Man Utd 5-1 Fulham |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2006-08-20 |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2012-11-05 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BwG2XfPM?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/4786577.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，又因雙腳飛踢[[瑞恩·吉格斯|-{zh-hans:吉格斯; zh-hk:傑斯;}-]]而遭受[[傳媒|傳媒]]的責難，但被[[黃牌|黃牌]]警告的布朗沒有受到進一步的懲罰<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.whoateallthepies.tv/fulham/269/michael_browns_.html |title=Michael Brown's two footed lunge at Giggs » Who Ate all the Pies |publisher=''Whoateallthepies.tv'' |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2018-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181030170423/http://www.whoateallthepies.tv/fulham/269/michael_browns_.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UNugWnNjwwg |title=‪Brown tackle on Giggs‬‏ |publisher=''[[YouTube|YouTube]]'' |date=2006-08-23 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2021-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515222204/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UNugWnNjwwg |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006年9月23日「西倫敦打吡」主場對[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]，雖然以0-2落敗，布朗仍然有好表現，美中不足是他再次雙腳飛踢[[艾殊利·高爾|艾殊利·高爾]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/5351934.stm |title=Fulham 0-2 Chelsea |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2006-09-23 |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2021-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115181552/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/5351934.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.fulhamweb.co.uk/news/Brown-defends-Cole-tackle.aspx |title=Fulham FC:Brown defends Cole tackle - Fulham FC Latest News |publisher=''Fulhamweb.co.uk'' |date=2006-09-25 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2018-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714164316/http://www.fulhamweb.co.uk/news/brown-defends-cole-tackle.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>，幸而球證[[马克·哈尔西|哈尔西]]（Mark Halsey）沒有看到事發經過而不予追究<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.fulhamweb.co.uk/news/Ref-Halsey-comments-on-Brown-tackle.aspx |title=Fulham FC:Ref Halsey comments on Brown tackle - Fulham FC Latest News |publisher=''Fulhamweb.co.uk'' |date=2006-09-26 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2018-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714135320/http://www.fulhamweb.co.uk/news/ref-halsey-comments-on-brown-tackle.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但在2006年結束前，富咸領隊[[基斯·高文|基斯·高文]]（Chris Coleman）出人意表地委任布朗成為球隊的[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]，雖然外界質疑這次任命，但他以表現贏取富咸球迷的信心。布朗憑藉改善的演出和永不言敗的精神而取得更多上陣的機會，保持隊長臂章直至球季結束。

[[2007年至2008年英格蘭超級聯賽|2007/08年球季]]前[[北愛爾蘭足球代表隊|北愛國家隊]]領隊[[羅里·山齊士|羅里·山齊士]]（Lawrie Sanchez）代替基斯·高文執掌帥印，重整軍容簽入多名新球員，包括[[迪奥曼西·卡马拉|-{zh-hans:迪奥曼西·卡马拉; zh-hk:D.卡馬拉;}-]]、[[大衛·希利|大衛·希利]]、[[克里斯·拜尔德|-{zh-hans:拜尔德; zh-hk:拜亞特;}-]]、[[保罗·孔切斯基|-{zh-hans:孔切斯基; zh-hk:高捷斯基;}-]]、[[艾朗·曉士|-{zh-hans:阿隆·休斯; zh-hk:艾朗·曉士;}-]]、[[李爾·曲克|李爾·曲克]]及[[史提芬·戴維斯|史提芬·戴維斯]]（Steven Davis），布朗因而成為球隊的清洗目標<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/sport/article-23405644-brown-set-to-decide-on-wigan-switch.do |title=Brown set to decide on Wigan switch |publisher=''Thisislondon.co.uk'' |date= |accessdate=2011-07-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120912025803/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/sport/article-23405644-brown-set-to-decide-on-wigan-switch.do |archivedate=2012-09-12 |df= }}</ref>。

;韋根
2007年7月31日布朗轉投另一支[[英超|英超]]球隊[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]，簽約三年，轉會費沒有透露<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wigan_athletic/6913938.stm |title=Brown completes transfer to Wigan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2007-07-31 |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2020-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016223914/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wigan_athletic/6913938.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但負責羅致他的領隊[[基斯·赫澄斯|基斯·赫澄斯]]（Chris Hutchings）不久後即被辭退，在新領隊[[史蒂夫·布鲁斯|布魯士]]麾下他與[[李·卡特摩尔|卡達莫]]及[[威尔森·帕拉西奥斯|柏拉西奧斯]]組成一條硬朗的中場線<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.wiganer.net/rprt/mtch/wigan_athletic_3_blackburn_rovers_0_421970/index.shtml |title=Wigan Athletic 3 Blackburn Rovers 0 - Wigan Athletic FC |publisher=''WIGANER.net'' |date=2008-12-13 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111003094831/http://www.wiganer.net/rprt/mtch/wigan_athletic_3_blackburn_rovers_0_421970/index.shtml |archivedate=2011-10-03 }}</ref>。在韋根逗留兩個球季專注防守工作，在各項賽事合共上陣64場沒有取得入球，但卻有18面[[黃牌|黃牌]]進帳。

;樸茨茅夫
2009年夏季韋根領隊布魯士轉投[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]，接手的[[罗伯托·马丁内斯|馬天尼斯]]於帶領[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]時以亮麗的進攻足球著稱，布朗並非其喜歡的球員類型，他因此於8月28日以象徵費用加盟[[英超|英超]]球會[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/8226466.stm |title=Portsmouth wrap up four signings |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-08-28 |accessdate=2011-07-15 |archive-date=2021-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106042113/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/8226466.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是他第二度效力這支南岸球隊，於10年前曾以借用身份上陣4場。8月30日首度披甲在主場0-1負於母會[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8222249.stm |title=Portsmouth 0-1 Man City |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-08-30 |accessdate=2011-07-15 |archive-date=2020-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200112202508/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8222249.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；10月17日主場對舊東家[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]，布朗遭兩[[黃牌|黃]]一[[紅牌|紅]]驅逐離場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=1056&season_id=139 |title=Portsmouth 1-2 Tottenham |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-10-17 |accessdate=2011-07-15 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924134247/http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=1056&season_id=139 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但他於2010年4月11日在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]的[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]準決賽協助樸茨茅夫以2-0淘汰熱刺，報卻一敗之辱並晉身決賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/8611101.stm |title=Tottenham 0-2 Portsmouth |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-04-11 |accessdate=2011-07-15 |archive-date=2021-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511013837/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/8611101.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；而較早前布朗曾於作客對[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]時被對方[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]][[史提芬·謝拉特|謝拉特]]以[[肘|手掙]]撞中面部<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Liverpool-captain-Steven-Gerrard-in-dock-over-clash-with-Portsmouth-s-Michael-Brown-article356861.html |title=Liverpool captain Steven Gerrard in dock over clash with Portsmouth's Michael Brown |publisher=''MirrorFootball.co.uk'' |date=2010-03-16 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116095804/http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Liverpool-captain-Steven-Gerrard-in-dock-over-clash-with-Portsmouth-s-Michael-Brown-article356861.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZJyOqJ5VLvA&NR=1 |title=‪Steven Gerrard elbows Michael Brown‬‏ |publisher=''[[YouTube|YouTube]]'' |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2014-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625034904/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZJyOqJ5VLvA&NR=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月18日已篤定降班的樸茨茅夫於主場1-2再負於[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]腳下，布朗為球隊先拔頭籌兼取得加盟後首球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8622625.stm |title=Portsmouth 1–2 Aston Villa |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=18 April 2010 |accessdate=18 April 2010}}</ref>；5月1日聯賽煞科日主場對[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]，布朗射入球隊降班前最後一球鎖定3-1勝局<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8647245.stm |title=Portsmouth 3-1 Wolverhampton |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-05-01 |accessdate=2011-07-15 |archive-date=2019-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190728165049/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8647245.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年5月10日在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]舉行[[2010年英格蘭足總杯決賽|足總盃決賽]]，面對已取得[[2009年至2010年英格蘭超級聯賽|聯賽]]兼以衛冕身份出賽的[[切尔西足球俱乐部|車路士]]，布朗正選上陣與[[帕帕·博巴·迪奥普|柏巴·迪奧普]]擔任防守中場，[[奇雲-派斯·保定|奇雲·保定]]的[[十二碼|十二碼]]遭[[佩特·切赫|施治]]救出，雖然藍軍亦有[[法蘭·林柏特|林柏特]]十二碼宴客兼5度射中門楣門柱，但憑[[迪迪埃·德罗巴|杜奧巴]]的入球僅勝1-0使車路士成為第7支贏得國內[[雙料冠軍|雙料冠軍]]的球隊，樸茨茅夫未能完成童話結局帶著一絲遺憾降班[[英冠|英冠]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/8680493.stm |title=Chelsea 1-0 Portsmouth |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-05-15 |accessdate=2011-07-15 |archive-date=2016-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230194207/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/8680493.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

樸茨茅夫遭遇嚴重財困兼降班後大將星散，領隊[[艾林·格蘭|艾林·格蘭]]亦另謀高就，換上[[史蒂夫·科特里爾|史蒂夫·科特里爾]]（Steve Cotterill）接手執教，布朗是少數留隊繼續打拼的球員之一。[[樸茨茅夫2010年至2011年球季|2010/11年球季]]布朗上陣24場及射入3球，他延續上季末的好腳風，於2010年8月9日在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第一圈作客2-1淘汰[[史提芬納治足球會|史提芬納治]]為球隊射入奠勝球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/8882540.stm |title=Stevenage 1-2 Portsmouth |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-08-09 |accessdate=2011- |archive-date=2019-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203022217/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/8882540.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；9月24日主場6-1大勝[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]再入1球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9020826.stm |title=Portsmouth 6-1 Leicester |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-09-24 |accessdate=2011-07-15 |archive-date=2021-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420092817/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9020826.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；10月16日主場對[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]，布朗於完場前10分鐘在禁區邊緣射入奠勝球鎖定3-2勝果<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9085096.stm |title=Portsmouth 3-2 Watford |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-10-16 |accessdate=2011-07-15 |archive-date=2013-01-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Dayv75MC?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9085096.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

他一直是球隊的中場重心，最後一次上陣是於[[节礼日|拆禮物日]]主場1-1賽和[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9309379.stm |title=Portsmouth 1-1 Millwall |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-26 |accessdate=2011-07-15 |archive-date=2018-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181211085535/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9309379.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其時他與隊友[[理查德·休斯|-{zh-hans:理查德·休斯; zh-hk:李察·曉士;}-]]（Richard Hughes）尚欠一場便會啟動合約條款自動續約，據報布朗新合約的週薪達到25,000[[英鎊|英鎊]]，是當時樸茨茅夫的財力不可能負擔的數目<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/3561763/Portsmouths-Michael-Brown-is-holding-transfer-talks-with-Middlesbrough-and-Hull-City.html |title=Portsmouth’s Michael Brown is holding transfer talks with Middlesbrough and Hull City |publisher=''thesun.co.uk'' |date=2011-05-04 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728054437/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/3561763/Portsmouths-Michael-Brown-is-holding-transfer-talks-with-Middlesbrough-and-Hull-City.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，領隊科特里爾對不能選派兩人上陣感到失望<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/9282302.stm |title=Contract clauses hinder Portsmouth boss Cotterill |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-13 |accessdate=2011-07-11}}</ref>，有傳[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]於未能成功羅致[[史提夫·薛維爾|薛維爾]]後希望簽入布朗<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1345182/Wolves-ready-revive-bid-Portsmouths-Michael-Brown.html |title=Wolves ready to revive bid for Portsmouth's Michael Brown |publisher=''Dailymail.co.uk'' |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2016-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160803053555/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1345182/Wolves-ready-revive-bid-Portsmouths-Michael-Brown.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]亦一度對他有意思<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Nottingham-Forest-transfer-news-Forest-ready-to-rescue-Portsmouth-pay-rebel-Michael-Brown-from-his-contract-limbo-article700859.html |title=Nottingham Forest transfer news Forest ready to rescue Portsmouth pay rebel Michael Brown from his contract limbo |publisher=''MirrorFootball.co.uk'' |date=2011-02-17 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2012-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015211301/http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Nottingham-Forest-transfer-news-Forest-ready-to-rescue-Portsmouth-pay-rebel-Michael-Brown-from-his-contract-limbo-article700859.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但直到[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]關閉後亦沒有落實轉會，2011年1月4日球會行政總裁大衛·林必特（David Lampitt）透露向兩人開出合理條件的新合約但被拒<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/9336993.stm |title=Lampitt confirms offers made to Brown and Hughes |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-04 |accessdate=2011-05-14 |archive-date=2019-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218163540/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/9336993.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而兩人亦沒有再為樸茨茅夫再上陣<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.football.co.uk/portsmouth/players/michael_brown_2708.shtml |title=Michael Brown - Portsmouth Football Club |publisher=''Football.co.uk'' |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2012-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120203003130/http://www.football.co.uk/portsmouth/players/michael_brown_2708.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/sport/pompey/pompey-past/great-matches/lampitt_no_january_sales_at_pompey_1_2358546 |title=Lampitt: No January sales at Pompey |publisher=''Portsmouth.co.uk'' |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2012-09-10 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120910074559/http://www.portsmouth.co.uk/sport/pompey/pompey-past/great-matches/lampitt_no_january_sales_at_pompey_1_2358546 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，直到5月13日樸茨茅夫宣佈於布朗的合約在6月30日屆滿後放棄續聘<ref name="Release">{{cite news |language=en |title=Ten players shown door by Portsmouth |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/13391018.stm |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-13 |accessdate=2011-05-13}}</ref>。他隨即與[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]及老上司尼爾·禾諾克執教的[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]扯上關係<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.mfc.co.uk/page/news/latest/0,,1~1492270,00.html |title=LINKED LIST: Dale Makes A Team |publisher=''Mfc.co.uk'' |date= |accessdate=2011-07-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710091143/http://www.mfc.co.uk/page/news/latest/0,,1~1492270,00.html |archivedate=2011-07-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Veteran-midfielder-Michael-Brown-is-keen-on-reunion-with-his-old-Sheffield-United-boss-Neil-Warnock-at-newly-promoted-QPR-following-his-release-by-Portsmouth-article737466.html |title=Veteran midfielder Michael Brown is keen on reunion with his old Sheffield United boss Neil Warnock at newly-promoted QPR following his release by Portsmouth |publisher=''MirrorFootball.co.uk'' |date=2011-05-17 |accessdate=2011-07-11 |archive-date=2012-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015211208/http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Veteran-midfielder-Michael-Brown-is-keen-on-reunion-with-his-old-Sheffield-United-boss-Neil-Warnock-at-newly-promoted-QPR-following-his-release-by-Portsmouth-article737466.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，直至2011年7月10日《[[星期日泰晤士報|星期日泰晤士報]]》報導布朗即將加盟[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]。

